trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when a SQL Server database is not enabled to support dependencies associated with the <xref href="System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: SQL Server 数据库未启用与关联的依赖项的支持时引发的异常<xref href="System.Web.Caching.SqlCacheDependency"></xref>类。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Caching.DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException"></xref> class.
The DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException creates a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.Caching.DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException> class with all fields set to their default values.
trans-unit.target: DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException 创建的新实例<xref:System.Web.Caching.DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException>所有字段都设置为其默认值的类。</xref:System.Web.Caching.DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Caching.DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException"></xref> class.
A string that describes the error.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Caching.DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException"></xref> class with a specified error message and a reference to the inner exception that is the cause of this exception.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.Web.Caching.DatabaseNotEnabledForNotificationException"></xref>使用指定的错误消息和对导致此异常的内部异常的引用的类。

trans-unit.source: The error message that explains the reason for the exception.
trans-unit.target: 解释异常原因的错误消息。

trans-unit.source: The exception that is the cause of the current exception.
If the `innerException` parameter is not <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, the current exception is raised in a catch block that handles the inner exception.
trans-unit.target: 如果`innerException`参数不是<xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>，处理内部异常的 catch 块中引发当前异常。
